### ── FAVORITES SERVICE (/favorites) ────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. Favorilere ekle — Customer Bauer, Porsche 911
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 2. Favorilere ekle — Customer Bauer, Tesla Model Y
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000025"
}

### 3. Favorileri listele — entity üzerinden
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/Favorites
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Favorileri listele — fonksiyon üzerinden
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/listFavorites()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 5. Aynı aracı tekrar ekle — reddedilmeli (duplicate)
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 6. Favorilerden çıkar — Porsche 911
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/removeFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 7. Favori listesi — Porsche 911 artık olmamalı
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/listFavorites()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 8. Customer Hoffmann'ın favorilerini görme — reddedilmeli
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/Favorites
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}